parts.text:
Magpie
```json
{
  "application": "Magpie",
  "software": [
    {
      "name": "Alluxio",
      "version": "2.3.0",
      "required": true,
      "setup": true,
      "configuration": {
        "ALLUXIO_HOME": "${HOME}/alluxio-${ALLUXIO_VERSION}",
        "ALLUXIO_WORKER_ON_MASTER": "yes",
        "ALLUXIO_LOCAL_DIR": "/tmp/${USER}/alluxio",
        "ALLUXIO_UNDER_FS_DIR": "/lustre/${USER}/alluxio",
        "ALLUXIO_DATA_CLEAR": "yes",
        "ALLUXIO_WORKER_MEMORY_SIZE": "16GB",
        "ALLUXIO_WORKER_TIER0_PATH": "/mnt/ramdisk",
        "ALLUXIO_RAMFS_MOUNT_OPTION": "SudoMount",
        "ALLUXIO_READ_TYPE": "CACHE",
        "ALLUXIO_WRITE_TYPE": "CACHE_THROUGH",
        "ALLUXIO_JOB": "testalluxio"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Java",
      "version": "1.8.0",
      "required": true,
      "setup": false,
      "configuration": {
        "JAVA_HOME": "/usr/lib/jvm/jre-1.8.0/"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Python",
      "version": "3",
      "required": true,
      "setup": false,
      "configuration": {
        "MAGPIE_PYTHON": "/usr/bin/python3"
      }
    }
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "scheduler": "SLURM",
    "node_count": "<my_node_count>",
    "time_limit": "<my_time_in_minutes>",
    "job_name": "<my_job_name>",
    "partition": "<my_partition>",
    "remote_shell": "ssh",
    "remote_shell_options": ""
  },
  "general_configuration": {
    "MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME": "${HOME}/magpie",
    "MAGPIE_LOCAL_DIR": "/tmp/${USER}/magpie",
    "MAGPIE_JOB_TYPE": "alluxio",
    "MAGPIE_ONE_TIME_RUN": "yes",
    "MAGPIE_PRE_JOB_RUN": null,
    "MAGPIE_POST_JOB_RUN": null,
    "MAGPIE_PRE_EXECUTE_RUN": null,
    "MAGPIE_POST_EXECUTE_RUN": null,
    "MAGPIE_ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLE_SCRIPT": null,
    "MAGPIE_ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLE_SCRIPT_SHELL": null,
    "MAGPIE_HOSTNAME_CMD": "hostname",
    "MAGPIE_SUBMISSION_TYPE": "sbatchmpirun",
    "MPIRUN_OPTIONS": "-genvall -genv MV2_USE_APM 0"
  }
}
```
